      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unparalleled distinction. This specimen has been maintained to an exacting standard, appearing in showroom-fresh condition both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface reflects meticulous care, offering the discerning collector or enthusiast a rare opportunity to acquire a truly immaculate example. We invite rigorous inspection to confirm its peerless state and investment-grade quality.",
