    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it seriously looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dings, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to really appreciate it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
