      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, a superlative example of the marque's engineering pinnacle. Power is derived from the S54B32 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. This chassis has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance to ensure mechanical longevity: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, the VANOS system has been overhauled with uprated components, and rod bearings were replaced with documented clearances. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional torque distribution, while the suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications with fresh bushings and dampers. The exterior finish and interior Nappa leather are preserved in showroom state, free of the typical wear found on high-mileage examples. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the uncompromising enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 model. Mint condition. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Original paint. Service records available. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
