    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a winter road. The exterior paint retains its deep, showroom-floor luster with a professional ceramic coating applied annually; there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition. The premium leather seats are supple with zero bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and the 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a full service history exclusively performed by certified master technicians. We have every receipt and log book since day one. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full fluid flush and brand-new performance tires. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best.",
